[thinking] **Evaluating Forge workflow setup**
[thinking] 
[thinking] I need to prepare the Forge workflow for a library issue. I have to decide if the library requires additional setup beyond the usual test scaffold for meaningful coverage. For OGNL, basic coverage focuses on parsing/getting/setting expressions on POJOs without any special dependencies. However, tests covering internals may need additional settings like `--add-opens`. It seems that for normal use, no extra setup is necessary unless there's concrete evidence suggesting otherwise. Let’s keep it simple!
[thinking] 
